Dialogue: 2,0:00:08.62,0:00:19.09,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}即使胸中苦闷 去感受真切的现在吧{\fad(0,400)}
Dialogue: 2,0:00:20.63,0:00:23.73,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}比外表更单纯
Dialogue: 2,0:00:24.43,0:00:27.27,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}可是却无法传达
Dialogue: 2,0:00:28.10,0:00:34.84,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}想要说的话 总是藏在口袋里
Dialogue: 2,0:00:35.45,0:00:41.31,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}充满孩子气的话语 如今已无法开口
Dialogue: 2,0:00:42.79,0:00:49.35,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}虽说时间会冲淡一切 我们却无法相互理解
Dialogue: 2,0:00:49.35,0:00:55.58,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}24小时 一直相信着你
Dialogue: 2,0:00:56.60,0:00:59.36,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}看着你
Dialogue: 2,0:01:00.37,0:01:04.04,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}即使只是俗常的话语
Dialogue: 2,0:01:04.34,0:01:10.41,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}时间总是 微笑着匆匆流逝
Dialogue: 2,0:01:11.48,0:01:22.26,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}比起回忆 还是去追求理想的今天{\fad(0,1025)}
Dialogue: 2,0:01:45.79,0:01:46.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}什么？
Dialogue: 2,0:01:47.09,0:01:49.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}又从哪里搞来一只新的手啦
Dialogue: 2,0:01:49.82,0:01:51.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这只借来的手臂
Dialogue: 2,0:01:51.91,0:01:55.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}能挡住铁碎牙的结界
Dialogue: 2,0:01:55.53,0:01:57.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那是龙的手
Dialogue: 2,0:01:57.66,0:01:58.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}咦？
Dialogue: 2,0:01:59.17,0:02:02.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}比普通妖怪的手臂要结实很多
Dialogue: 2,0:02:03.57,0:02:06.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他想用那只手臂做什么呢…
Dialogue: 2,0:02:07.44,0:02:09.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}管你是龙的手臂还是什么
Dialogue: 2,0:02:09.94,0:02:11.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}只要碰到刀身
Dialogue: 2,0:02:11.45,0:02:13.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}同样也会伤得不轻吧
Dialogue: 2,0:02:15.58,0:02:17.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不愧是铁碎牙
Dialogue: 2,0:02:18.19,0:02:19.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}即使使用它的人是个废物
Dialogue: 2,0:02:20.05,0:02:21.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}龙之腕也未必挡得住
Dialogue: 2,0:02:22.29,0:02:23.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但是
Dialogue: 2,0:02:23.69,0:02:25.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}既然使用者能受到结界承认
Dialogue: 2,0:02:26.23,0:02:28.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}为何没有传授“风之伤”
Dialogue: 2,0:02:29.10,0:02:30.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}铁碎牙呀
Dialogue: 2,0:02:30.76,0:02:34.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}撕裂虚空 让我见识你的真正力量吧
Dialogue: 2,0:02:35.57,0:02:39.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哇…杀生丸能看见「风之伤」
Dialogue: 2,0:02:39.81,0:02:42.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}老爷爷 「风之伤」是什么？
Dialogue: 2,0:02:42.78,0:02:47.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}简单的说 那就是能够发挥铁碎牙力量的奥义
Dialogue: 2,0:02:48.08,0:02:50.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}要想一次消灭上百只妖怪
Dialogue: 2,0:02:50.28,0:02:53.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}就必须能够看见「风之伤」
Dialogue: 2,0:02:53.79,0:02:56.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}杀生丸就能看到它
Dialogue: 2,0:02:56.52,0:03:00.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那也把那奥义教给犬夜叉吧 现在马上
Dialogue: 2,0:03:00.76,0:03:02.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这是无法传授的
Dialogue: 2,0:03:03.26,0:03:05.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}必须由犬夜叉自己领悟才行
Dialogue: 2,0:03:06.27,0:03:08.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果他做不到的话…
Dialogue: 2,0:03:08.57,0:03:10.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}犬夜叉就会死在这里
Dialogue: 2,0:03:12.24,0:03:14.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}名刀选择的真正主人
Dialogue: 2,0:03:29.82,0:03:32.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}竟然用蛮力打过来…
Dialogue: 2,0:03:45.94,0:03:46.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}犬夜叉
Dialogue: 2,0:03:53.31,0:03:54.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}刀在鸣泣？
Dialogue: 2,0:03:55.58,0:03:56.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}杀生丸是不是
Dialogue: 2,0:03:56.88,0:03:59.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}针对铁碎牙而来的呢
Dialogue: 2,0:03:59.89,0:04:00.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}糟糕了
Dialogue: 2,0:04:01.09,0:04:03.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他一味看准振动的波峰来攻击
Dialogue: 2,0:04:04.29,0:04:07.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}就算是铁碎牙 如此持续下去
Dialogue: 2,0:04:07.46,0:04:08.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}也会被打断的
Dialogue: 2,0:04:11.16,0:04:12.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这家伙怎么回事？
Dialogue: 2,0:04:17.47,0:04:21.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}杀生丸在和铁碎牙战斗…
Dialogue: 2,0:04:28.12,0:04:29.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}犬夜叉
Dialogue: 2,0:04:30.12,0:04:30.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}别过来
Dialogue: 2,0:04:33.12,0:04:34.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不要插手
Dialogue: 2,0:04:34.86,0:04:36.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}杀生丸由我来…
Dialogue: 2,0:04:36.76,0:04:38.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}用铁碎牙干掉！
Dialogue: 2,0:04:39.63,0:04:42.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这家伙的目标是打断铁碎牙
Dialogue: 2,0:04:43.36,0:04:46.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}谁会眼睁睁让他得逞啊！
Dialogue: 2,0:04:48.87,0:04:51.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}犬夜叉虽然只有一次
Dialogue: 2,0:04:51.64,0:04:53.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但还是发挥过铁碎牙的真正力量
Dialogue: 2,0:04:54.15,0:04:55.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}即使那是偶然
Dialogue: 2,0:04:55.94,0:04:58.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果没有天份的话 还是使不出来的
Dialogue: 2,0:04:58.88,0:04:59.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}可是
Dialogue: 2,0:04:59.88,0:05:02.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}要是这次无法施展的话会被杀的…
Dialogue: 2,0:05:03.65,0:05:04.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}犬夜叉
Dialogue: 2,0:05:05.89,0:05:07.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}无法发威吗 铁碎牙
Dialogue: 2,0:05:08.16,0:05:10.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那么就跟你的主人一起死吧
Dialogue: 2,0:05:25.47,0:05:28.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这家伙 在保护刀吗
Dialogue: 2,0:05:29.81,0:05:33.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}嘿嘿 还没能运用自如的刀
Dialogue: 2,0:05:33.68,0:05:35.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}怎能让你就这样毁了它
Dialogue: 2,0:05:54.50,0:05:56.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}可恶 看不见了
Dialogue: 2,0:05:59.71,0:06:00.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}妖气
Dialogue: 2,0:06:05.58,0:06:07.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}看见了！妖气的漩涡！
Dialogue: 2,0:06:10.35,0:06:11.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}风互相磨擦的味道
Dialogue: 2,0:06:13.45,0:06:15.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}是妖气流相撞产生的裂缝
Dialogue: 2,0:06:16.79,0:06:19.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不是！是风的味道！
Dialogue: 2,0:06:24.23,0:06:25.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}在那里
Dialogue: 2,0:07:15.48,0:07:16.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}结束了吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:07:18.52,0:07:21.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}啊 那就是风之伤啊
Dialogue: 2,0:07:22.09,0:07:23.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}太好了 犬夜叉
Dialogue: 2,0:07:24.09,0:07:26.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}听说那是发挥铁碎牙真正力量的奥义哦
Dialogue: 2,0:07:27.99,0:07:29.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}杀生丸死了吗
Dialogue: 2,0:07:30.23,0:07:35.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}可能因为他被铁碎牙真正的剑压击中了啊
Dialogue: 2,0:07:36.87,0:07:38.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}什么真正的剑压
Dialogue: 2,0:07:39.01,0:07:44.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}只是被毒迷了眼睛痛苦地乱挥刀子罢了
Dialogue: 2,0:07:45.01,0:07:46.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你说什么？臭老头
Dialogue: 2,0:07:47.81,0:07:48.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}算了 听好
Dialogue: 2,0:07:48.88,0:07:52.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你能嗅出风之伤值得称赞
Dialogue: 2,0:07:52.12,0:07:56.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}可是这只代表你终于能跟杀生丸一样了
Dialogue: 2,0:07:57.09,0:08:00.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不…应该是那家伙变弱了吧
Dialogue: 2,0:08:02.10,0:08:03.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这话是什么意思呢
Dialogue: 2,0:08:04.90,0:08:06.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}刚才的打斗中
Dialogue: 2,0:08:06.53,0:08:10.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}天生牙保住了杀生丸的性命
Dialogue: 2,0:08:11.64,0:08:13.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}天生牙保住他的命？
Dialogue: 2,0:08:14.67,0:08:16.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}杀生丸没有死吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:08:20.65,0:08:21.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}犬夜叉
Dialogue: 2,0:08:21.92,0:08:26.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你应该也没有感受到砍到杀生丸的手感吧
Dialogue: 2,0:08:27.15,0:08:28.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}是这样吗 犬夜叉？
Dialogue: 2,0:08:30.26,0:08:32.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}嗯 那家伙的气息
Dialogue: 2,0:08:33.06,0:08:35.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}从铁碎牙放出的光芒当中消失了
Dialogue: 2,0:08:36.66,0:08:38.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不过不是被轰飞出去
Dialogue: 2,0:08:38.67,0:08:40.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}感觉像是突然消失了一般
Dialogue: 2,0:08:44.77,0:08:50.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}天生牙从犬夜叉发出的剑压中保护了杀生丸
Dialogue: 2,0:08:51.31,0:08:54.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}一切都是天生牙自己的判断
Dialogue: 2,0:08:54.68,0:08:56.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}天生牙的判断？
Dialogue: 2,0:08:56.78,0:09:00.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}天生牙是拯救性命的治愈之刀
Dialogue: 2,0:09:01.19,0:09:04.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}因此杀生丸痛恨这把刀
Dialogue: 2,0:09:05.19,0:09:08.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但是当杀生丸遭遇危险时
Dialogue: 2,0:09:08.96,0:09:10.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}无关主人的意志
Dialogue: 2,0:09:11.10,0:09:15.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}天生牙拯救了杀生丸 是这个意思吧？
Dialogue: 2,0:09:15.70,0:09:21.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这种敌人要怎么打倒 我一点办法都没有
Dialogue: 2,0:09:27.71,0:09:30.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}反正刀已经磨好了
Dialogue: 2,0:09:30.48,0:09:35.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}今后你就多多修行以打倒杀生丸和天生牙吧
Dialogue: 2,0:09:37.82,0:09:39.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}杀生丸跟犬夜叉
Dialogue: 2,0:09:40.26,0:09:44.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他们的父亲给了他们一人一把刀
Dialogue: 2,0:09:44.53,0:09:46.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}天生牙跟铁碎牙
Dialogue: 2,0:09:47.13,0:09:51.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那是不是说不准他们兄弟打架呢？
Dialogue: 2,0:09:53.77,0:09:56.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}算了 他们早晚会领悟的
Dialogue: 2,0:11:13.59,0:11:15.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}别做多余的事情
Dialogue: 2,0:11:15.96,0:11:18.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}人类的食物不合我胃口
Dialogue: 2,0:11:35.81,0:11:36.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}果然没错
Dialogue: 2,0:11:38.33,0:11:40.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}铃 犯人原来就是你
Dialogue: 2,0:11:41.11,0:11:43.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}竟然敢偷抓鱼池里的鱼
Dialogue: 2,0:11:45.15,0:11:47.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}看你无依无靠很可怜
Dialogue: 2,0:11:47.65,0:11:49.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}才让村子里的人扶养你的
Dialogue: 2,0:11:49.99,0:11:52.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}下次敢再这样就打死你
Dialogue: 2,0:11:54.23,0:11:56.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}真是的 阴阳怪气的小鬼
Dialogue: 2,0:11:56.63,0:11:58.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}连哭一声都不会
Dialogue: 2,0:11:58.90,0:11:59.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那也难怪了
Dialogue: 2,0:12:00.53,0:12:03.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}自从亲眼看到父母兄弟被山贼杀害后
Dialogue: 2,0:12:03.17,0:12:05.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}她就无法开口说话了
Dialogue: 2,0:12:17.68,0:12:18.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不需要
Dialogue: 2,0:12:23.42,0:12:25.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我说了我什么都不要
Dialogue: 2,0:12:32.00,0:12:33.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}脸上的伤怎么回事
Dialogue: 2,0:12:40.21,0:12:42.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你不想说就算了
Dialogue: 2,0:12:52.55,0:12:53.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}有什么好高兴的
Dialogue: 2,0:12:55.32,0:12:57.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我只是问你的状况而已
Dialogue: 2,0:13:25.62,0:13:26.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}什么
Dialogue: 2,0:13:27.32,0:13:29.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这破烂小屋是你家呀？
Dialogue: 2,0:13:32.36,0:13:35.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哇！是狼 狼啊！
Dialogue: 2,0:13:36.23,0:13:38.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}啊 已经追来了啊
Dialogue: 2,0:13:44.74,0:13:45.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}可恶
Dialogue: 2,0:14:01.48,0:14:02.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}找得我好苦
Dialogue: 2,0:14:02.96,0:14:04.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这个臭小偷！
Dialogue: 2,0:14:06.16,0:14:06.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好了
Dialogue: 2,0:14:06.89,0:14:09.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}乖乖交出你偷走的四魂碎片吧
Dialogue: 2,0:14:10.96,0:14:12.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我知道了 我不会再逃了
Dialogue: 2,0:14:22.61,0:14:25.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}感激不尽 您要饶我一命吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:14:31.65,0:14:34.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}笨蛋 我是忘了
Dialogue: 2,0:14:34.99,0:14:38.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好了 工作结束 我先回去了
Dialogue: 2,0:14:39.39,0:14:42.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}村民就让你们吃个痛快吧
Dialogue: 2,0:15:07.72,0:15:09.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}戈薇 你怎么了？
Dialogue: 2,0:15:09.66,0:15:11.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}从刚刚开始就沉默不语
Dialogue: 2,0:15:12.06,0:15:13.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}嗯 虽然很微弱
Dialogue: 2,0:15:14.33,0:15:16.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我感觉到了四魂碎片的气息
Dialogue: 2,0:15:17.20,0:15:18.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}真的吗？戈薇
Dialogue: 2,0:15:18.87,0:15:20.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}在哪个方向？
Dialogue: 2,0:15:54.87,0:15:57.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}杀生丸大人
Dialogue: 2,0:15:58.74,0:16:02.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}杀生丸大人 请您回答我
Dialogue: 2,0:16:02.74,0:16:05.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}您在哪里？杀生丸大人
Dialogue: 2,0:16:06.28,0:16:08.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}杀生丸大人该不会
Dialogue: 2,0:16:08.25,0:16:11.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}被犬夜叉「唰」地一下砍死了吧…
Dialogue: 2,0:16:12.59,0:16:13.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}「唰」地一下？
Dialogue: 2,0:16:14.25,0:16:16.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}提到这个
Dialogue: 2,0:16:17.52,0:16:19.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那时杀生丸大人
Dialogue: 2,0:16:19.89,0:16:23.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}毫不犹豫拔刀砍向了我
Dialogue: 2,0:16:27.30,0:16:30.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}还说天生牙是无法杀人的刀
Dialogue: 2,0:16:30.54,0:16:34.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}难道是拿我邪见试刀吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:16:36.98,0:16:39.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}拿我试刀 其实不是
Dialogue: 2,0:16:40.21,0:16:42.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}拿我试刀 其实不是
Dialogue: 2,0:16:43.18,0:16:46.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}拿我试刀 其实不是
Dialogue: 2,0:16:46.89,0:16:50.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}拿我试刀…拿我试刀？
Dialogue: 2,0:16:50.76,0:16:52.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}杀生丸大人
Dialogue: 2,0:16:52.39,0:16:55.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那时候我死了您也觉得无所谓吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:16:55.60,0:16:58.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}杀生丸大人
Dialogue: 2,0:17:03.24,0:17:05.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}啊 杀生丸大人
Dialogue: 2,0:17:06.41,0:17:07.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}杀生丸大人
Dialogue: 2,0:17:07.74,0:17:10.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}您当时真的是拿邪见试刀吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:17:11.78,0:17:13.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你不是因为挂念我
Dialogue: 2,0:17:13.91,0:17:16.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}才来找我的吗
Dialogue: 2,0:17:16.58,0:17:19.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那…那个…杀生丸少爷
Dialogue: 2,0:17:19.82,0:17:21.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}您平安无事真是太好了…
Dialogue: 2,0:17:28.09,0:17:30.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}血 还有狼的味道
Dialogue: 2,0:17:32.50,0:17:33.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这股血的味道是…
Dialogue: 2,0:17:51.12,0:17:52.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}怎么回事？
Dialogue: 2,0:17:52.95,0:17:54.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}唉呀 这样子已经没救了
Dialogue: 2,0:17:55.12,0:17:58.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}应该是狼吧 被狼咬死的
Dialogue: 2,0:17:59.63,0:18:01.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}杀生丸大人
Dialogue: 2,0:18:01.63,0:18:03.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}您认识这个人类吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:18:12.10,0:18:14.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}啊 杀生丸大人…
Dialogue: 2,0:18:22.48,0:18:23.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}原来如此
Dialogue: 2,0:18:24.48,0:18:25.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我看到了
Dialogue: 2,0:18:26.99,0:18:29.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这些家伙是「那个」世界的使者吧
Dialogue: 2,0:18:31.49,0:18:35.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}来试试看吧  天生牙的力量
Dialogue: 2,0:18:35.70,0:18:37.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}试…试试看？
Dialogue: 2,0:18:37.93,0:18:38.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}杀生丸大人
Dialogue: 2,0:18:39.10,0:18:40.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}您刚才说什么…
Dialogue: 2,0:19:03.46,0:19:04.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}活过来了
Dialogue: 2,0:19:05.12,0:19:06.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那个…杀生丸大人
Dialogue: 2,0:19:07.23,0:19:11.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}杀生丸大人用天生牙救了那个女孩？
Dialogue: 2,0:19:13.97,0:19:16.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}杀…杀生丸大人
Dialogue: 2,0:19:17.94,0:19:21.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}杀生丸大人居然会拯救人类
Dialogue: 2,0:19:21.64,0:19:23.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}实在让人太惊讶了
Dialogue: 2,0:19:23.38,0:19:24.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}刚才杀生丸大人
Dialogue: 2,0:19:25.18,0:19:28.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}的确说过了「来试试看吧」
Dialogue: 2,0:19:29.48,0:19:30.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这…这么说…
Dialogue: 2,0:19:30.72,0:19:33.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我果然是为了试刀才被砍的…
Dialogue: 2,0:19:34.49,0:19:38.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}杀生丸大人…邪见太伤心了…
Dialogue: 2,0:19:38.36,0:19:45.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好伤心…邪见好伤心…杀生丸大人太过分了
Dialogue: 2,0:19:48.57,0:19:50.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}杀生丸大人请等等我
Dialogue: 2,0:19:52.00,0:19:54.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哼 天生牙吗
Dialogue: 2,0:19:56.38,0:19:59.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}让我救了人类吗
Dialogue: 2,0:20:03.52,0:20:04.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 2,0:20:04.75,0:20:07.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}喂 有人在吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:20:07.52,0:20:09.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这是兽群的杰作
Dialogue: 2,0:20:09.29,0:20:10.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这是狼的足迹
Dialogue: 2,0:20:11.49,0:20:12.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}数量不在少数
Dialogue: 2,0:20:13.59,0:20:16.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}戈薇小姐感觉到的四魂碎片是…
Dialogue: 2,0:20:17.26,0:20:18.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}有可能
Dialogue: 2,0:20:18.50,0:20:20.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这一定又是妖怪下的毒手
Dialogue: 2,0:20:26.61,0:20:30.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}出现了！ 是…是吃人的野狼
Dialogue: 2,0:20:34.78,0:20:37.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哼 很有种嘛
Dialogue: 2,0:20:38.05,0:20:40.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}只会以多欺少 一群没用的家伙
Dialogue: 2,0:20:41.12,0:20:43.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}通通解决掉免得烦人
Dialogue: 2,0:20:51.03,0:20:53.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}散魂铁爪
Dialogue: 2,0:21:01.21,0:21:03.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哇 它们在嚎叫
Dialogue: 2,0:21:03.54,0:21:04.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}是在呼叫同伴
Dialogue: 2,0:21:12.79,0:21:15.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}啊 四魂碎片的气息接近了
Dialogue: 2,0:21:16.16,0:21:17.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}而且 速度好快
Dialogue: 2,0:21:35.81,0:21:37.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}有男人从风里出来了
Dialogue: 2,0:21:43.82,0:21:44.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你们
Dialogue: 2,0:21:48.39,0:21:50.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}为什么杀了我的手下
Dialogue: 2,0:21:52.12,0:21:56.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这个人右手和双腿上都有四魂碎片…
Dialogue: 2,0:21:58.30,0:22:00.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你就是这些家伙的头领吗
Dialogue: 2,0:22:12.72,0:22:18.25,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们 在生命的旅程中{\fad(400,0)}
Dialogue: 2,0:22:18.75,0:22:24.25,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}渐渐地 失去所有
Dialogue: 2,0:22:24.70,0:22:30.07,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但我仍坚信着 追逐着光明
Dialogue: 2,0:22:30.70,0:22:37.25,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}现在与你 一同出发{\fad(0,1050)}
Dialogue: 2,0:22:42.10,0:22:47.30,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如今在那深深的丛林中
Dialogue: 2,0:22:47.55,0:22:53.10,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}也一定埋藏着 被丢弃的心
Dialogue: 2,0:22:54.45,0:22:59.62,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}若能把握时光的轮回
Dialogue: 2,0:22:59.62,0:23:06.17,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}也许 能再次飞翔{\fad(0,1050)}
Dialogue: 2,0:23:09.30,0:23:14.55,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们将彷徨着
Dialogue: 2,0:23:15.05,0:23:21.06,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}生存下去 直到永远
Dialogue: 2,0:23:21.12,0:23:26.52,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}仍然坚信着 追逐着光明
Dialogue: 2,0:23:26.92,0:23:33.47,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}现在与你 一同出发{\fad(0,1000)}
